dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Marina and Salinas quadrangles, Monterey County, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Marina, CA 1947, photorevised 1983, DMA 1657 III NE, Series V895 ; Salinas, CA 1947, photorevised 1968. AMS 1657 II NW, Series V895." "First printing, September 2007." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology. Includes "pertinent references", most recent published in 1999.
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
